  "title": "A round star-like UFO reported in Curitiba-PR [1992]",
  "URL": "http://brazilianufoarchives.com/2020/07/06/a-round-star-like-ufo-reported-in-curitiba-pr-1992/",
  "short_URL": "https://wp.me/pc3ctW-1pu",
  "content": "<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>DEC 2nd, 1992</strong>. Time: 20:00. Duration: 20 seconds. In Curitiba, State of Paraná, three people spotted an unidentified flying object with a round shape, &#8220;slightly larger than a star&#8221;, as seen in the sky. According to the witnesses, the UFO was a &#8220;continuous white light&#8221; at &#8220;very high speed&#8221;, flying towards the South of Curitiba. The witness estimated the UFO&#8217;s altitude at approximately 45,000 ft. The object was observed with the naked eye in a cloud-free sky.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>Cf.</em> ARQUIVO NACIONAL (Brasil). Sistema de Informações do Arquivo Nacional (SIAN). Fundo ‘Objeto Voador Não Identificado (OVNI)’. Código de Referência BR DFANBSB ARX.0.0.334. “Questionário sobre ocorrência de objeto voador não identificado na região de Curitiba, Estado do Paraná</span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">”. Brasília, DF. 1952 a 2015. Último acesso realizado em 27/05/2020.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">The BRAZILIAN UFO ARCHIVES website is a private initiative and IS NOT endorsed or sponsored by the Arquivo Nacional do Brasil [see our ‘Info’ page]. </span></em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>*THE ORIGINAL FILE WITH THE CASE REFERRED TO IN THIS TEXT CAN BE FOUND IN THE DOCUMENTAL COLLECTION OF “ARQUIVO NACIONAL DO BRASIL, LOCATED IN THE “OBJETO VOADOR NÃO IDENTIFICADO (OVNI)” FUND, UNDER THE REFERENCE CODE [“Código de Referência”] MENTIONED ABOVE.</em> <strong><a style=\"color:#808000;\" href=\"http://sian.an.gov.br/sianex/consulta/login.asp\">HERE IS THE LINK TO SEARCH THEIR WEBSITE</a></strong></span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"> </span>&lt;</p>\n",
  "excerpt": "<p>DEC 2nd, 1992. Time: 20:00. Duration: 20 seconds. In Curitiba, State of Paraná, three people spotted an unidentified flying object with a round shape, &#8220;slightly larger than a star&#8221;, as seen in the sky. According to the witnesses, the UFO was a &#8220;continuous white light&#8221; at &#8220;very high speed&#8221;, flying towards the South of Curitiba. [&hellip;]</p>\n",
